Fertile grasslands w/ light forestation in places, east of the West Wood, west of the Dorian Plains.

* Goldencross
- Largest city in the Copper Fields
- Central trade city, vibrant street vendors.
- Can buy pretty much anything there.
- Orderly, but groups of bandit types will go there to unwind, aren't paid much mind
- Farm focused - walk by farms for several miles surrounding the city

* Sevenmead
- Smaller town, south east of Goldencross
- Known for their bees / mead
- Fields of flowers, cultivated wildflowers and clovers
- Springtime festivals

* Titan's Fist
- Large, sheer stone protrusion
- Size of Rhode Island, a mile or so high - straight up
